Iterative Development and Responsibilities

This outlines the process for the project, and assigns certain things to certain people.

Make title screen appear
Make game state appear
Make ship moveable
Make aliens move
Player can shoot
Aliens can shoot
Register collisions (Shapte.intersects()) **Don't have to do logic yet, just register that there was a collision)
Colision logic
Setup lives (No need to make anything happen when lives == 0)
Game can be lost 
Game can be won
**BONUS**
Each level gets harder
Special alien at top